Install WCT

sudo npm install -g web-component-tester

In your project

bower install web-component-tester --save
#This will provide browser.js and mocha/chai test tools to write suites

Write tests for web-components
Check customelement/test for example (index.html -> basic.html and shadow.html)

For running tests
Navigate to customelement and run sudo wct

Another way to run tests is
Open URL
http://localhost:3000/labs/customelement/test/index.html
in different browser and evaluate.
